🔥 Sensitivity kya hoti hai?
👉 Sensitivity = koi access/data  kitna critical/secret/dangerous hai.

1️⃣ Example (Real Life):-
Company me different types ka data hota hai.
Data	          Sensitivity
Company news---------Low
Employee email------Medium
Salary details------High
Bank account-------Very High
Matlab:-
Jitna important data
utni high sensitivity

🧠 1. Sensitivity kaise decide karte hai?
🔹 (1) Data type pe:-
Bank / salary / personal data → HIGH sensitivity
Normal info (name, email) → LOW sensitivity

🔹 (2) Access type pe:-
Admin / Root access → HIGH
Read-only → LOW

🔹 (3) Application pe:-
SAP / DB / Finance system → HIGH
Email / Portal → MEDIUM

🔹 (4) Impact pe:-
Agar misuse se company ko loss ho → HIGH
No major impact → LOW
------------------------------
🔢 3. Formula se sensitivity (Advanced):-
👉 Agar tu calculate karna chahe:-
Sensitivity Score = (Data Impact + Access Level + App Criticality) / 3
🧠 Example:-
Data Impact     = 90   (salary data)
Access Level    = 80   (admin)
App Criticality = 70   (SAP)

👉 Calculation:-
Sensitivity = (90 + 80 + 70) / 3 = 80
-------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
📊 Formula weight:-
Weight = (Individual Risk / Total Risk) × 100
🧠 Example:-
Entitlement Risk = 80
Role Risk        = 40
Policy Risk      = 20
Total = 140

👉 Weight nikalo:-
Entitlement = (80/140) × 100 ≈ 57%
Role        = (40/140) × 100 ≈ 29%
Policy      = (20/140) × 100 ≈ 14%

⚖️ 1. Weight kaise niklega?
👉 Weight formula se nahi nikalta
👉 Weight tum decide karte ho (config/business rule se)

🧠 2. Decide kaise karte hai?
👉 Ye depend karta hai:-

🔹 (1) Sensitivity
High sensitive → weight zyada
Low sensitive → weight kam

🔹 (2) Business Impact
DB Admin access → high impact → high weight
Normal user → low weight

🔹 (3) Security Risk
Privileged access → 60–80%
Normal access → 10–20%

🎯 3. Practical Example
Company decide karti hai:-
Entitlement → 50%
Role        → 30%
Policy      → 20%
👉 Ye hi weight hai (ye nikala nahi, set kiya)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
RiskScore = (Entitlements Risk × weight)
          + (Role Risk × weight)
          + (Policy Risk × weight)